  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\nWe have several different names:\r\n- `:primary-name`\r\n- `:secondary-name`\r\n- `:display-name`\r\n- `:preferred-name`\r\n\r\nIt seems like only `:primary-name` and `:secondary-name` should be used across the app but there is no general concensus. \r\nThis PR https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/17384 radically simplified it all but there are still some leftovers of `:display-name` and `:preferred-name` which might lead to inconsistencies with how names are getting displayed.\r\n\r\n**UPD:**\r\nThere is a new function designed to always be used when the name is needed: it's `status-im2.contexts.profile.utils/displayed-name`. This issue might be just about replacing `:primary-name` and `:display-name` with this function.",
